<title>jrạḥ ḥbyby gẖạlyẗ ʿly̱</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - jrạḥ ḥbyby gẖạlyẗ ʿly kẖlytny ạ̉krh kl kẖṭyẗ
 wạ̉sẖtạq mn qlby ạ̉kẖdm ạlly ạ̉ḥsn ạ̹ly
 1- ʿyny ạ̹ly ạlḥml ạlmdẖbwḥ ạ̹rfʿny ạ̹rfʿny bạlrwḥ
 ( lky ạ̉qbl sr sẖfạỷy why ạljrwḥ )2
