 ( mạly ʿly ḥyạty wsẖạyfh bạlạ̹ymạn )2
 4- msyḥy ly mljạ̉ wqwẗ ʿwny fy ạlḍyq wmlysẖ gẖyr hw
 ( mn ḥbh sẖạyf ṣwrty̱ fy qlbh qlbh mn jwẗ)2
 5- hạtwạ rbạb bʿsẖr ạ̉wtạr wsbḥwạ mkẖlṣnạ ạlbạr
 ( ḥbyb ạlqlb ạlly bṣlybh ṣrnạ ạ̉ḥrạr )2</lyrics>
